  "scenario_brief": "Test Scenario: Table Items Feature\n\nDemonstrates placing notes and containers (bags with contents) on tables.\n\nTwo modes:\n  Mode B – no sprite/coords: pairs with the nth Tiled-map table in order.\n  Mode A – sprite and/or x/y set: creates a brand-new table at that position.\n\nIn both modes, items whose Tiled sprite is not from a table layer (e.g. bags,\nbriefcases) are repositioned so their bottom sits on the top half of the table.\n\nLayout:\n  [CEO Office - room_ceo2]\n         ↑\n  [Office - room_office2]",
